

#1 Update Mod function
	1. Divide l1 by l2 and store the result in one list
	2. Multiply the result from step 1 with step 2 and store in one list
	3. Subtract the result from step 2 from the list 1
	4. return the result of step 3

#2 Update error handling
	1. Make a character array in main and a error bool type variable, [Declare global array]
	2. Update error variable whenever needed as well as the error code
	3. any time the control is passed and error variable is true, keep returning NULL till main!
	4. print error message and reset the error variable.

